statements.sql: select * from `pages` where `is_active` = 1 and (json_contains(`slug`, '\"theme\\/turkbilisim23\\/assets\\/plugins\\/fontawesome-6.2.0\\/css\\/all.css\"', '$."tr"') or `slug` LIKE '%\"theme/turkbilisim23/assets/plugins/fontawesome-6.2.0/css/all.css\"%') and `pages`.`deleted_at` is null limit 1

select * from `portfolios` where `is_active` = 1 and (json_contains(`slug`, '\"theme\\/turkbilisim23\\/assets\\/plugins\\/fontawesome-6.2.0\\/css\\/all.css\"', '$."tr"') or `slug` LIKE '%\"theme/turkbilisim23/assets/plugins/fontawesome-6.2.0/css/all.css\"%') and `portfolios`.`deleted_at` is null limit 1

select * from `announcements` where `is_active` = 1 and (json_contains(`slug`, '\"theme\\/turkbilisim23\\/assets\\/plugins\\/fontawesome-6.2.0\\/css\\/all.css\"', '$."tr"') or `slug` LIKE '%\"theme/turkbilisim23/assets/plugins/fontawesome-6.2.0/css/all.css\"%') and `announcements`.`deleted_at` is null limit 1
select * from `portfolio_categories` where `is_active` = 1 and (json_contains(`slug`, '\"all.css\"', '$."tr"') or `slug` LIKE '%\"all.css\"%') and `portfolio_categories`.`deleted_at` is null limit 1
select * from `tenant_languages` where `is_active` = 1 order by `sort_order` asc limit 1
select query, MAX(slug) as slug, COUNT(*) as search_count from `search_queries` where `is_popular` = 1 and `is_hidden` = 0 group by `query` order by `search_count` desc limit 10
select * from `shop_categories` where `parent_id` is null and `is_active` = 1 and `shop_categories`.`deleted_at` is null order by `sort_order` asc
select * from `ai_tenant_directives` where `tenant_id` is null and `directive_key` = 'chatbot_quick_actions' and `is_active` = 1 limit 1
select * from `shop_categories` where `is_active` = 1 and `parent_id` is null and `shop_categories`.`deleted_at` is null order by `sort_order` asc limit 6
